OL,3,CWRU say 'don't gamble with Welsh
OL,4,CRugby's future' as they issue 'stark
OL,5,Cwarning'
OL,7,FThe Welsh Rugby Union has issued a
OL,8,F"stark warning" to member clubs not to
OL,9,F"gamble with Welsh Rugby's future".
OL,11,FIt comes after a letter from a single
OL,12,Fassociate member of the WRU (Central
OL,13,FGlamorgan) was circulated across Wales
OL,14,Fcalling for an Extraordinary General
OL,15,FMeeting or EGM.
OL,17,FIn a letter to other clubs, Central
OL,18,FGlamorgan tabled 3 motions including
OL,19,Fcalls for a vote of no confidence in
OL,20,Fthe Chair of the WRU, Richard Collier-
OL,21,FKeywood.
