OL,7,FThey added "any delay now means
OL,8,Fmissing the boat for men's and women's
OL,9,Frugby and undermining long term
OL,10,Fsuccess on the field.
OL,12,F"Financial stability, investment,
OL,13,Fgovernment backing, sponsorships and
OL,14,Fsupporter retention and growth depend
OL,15,Fon confidence in governance. An EGM
OL,16,Fwould put this at risk.
