OL,7,FTerry Cobner, President, Richard
OL,8,FCollier-Keywood, Chair and Abi
OL,9,FTierney, Chief Executive said to the
OL,10,FClubs: "This is not the moment to
OL,11,Fgamble with Welsh rugby's future with
OL,12,Fthe short-sighted and debilitating
OL,13,Fmotions that have been presented. We
OL,14,Fhave a plan. It was shaped by you. It
OL,15,Fis published. Let's deliver it
OL,16,Ftogether."
